title: Australia current and future climate data
description:
Current and future climate data for the Australian continent
Geographic extent: Australia
Year range: 1976-2005,2015-2085
Resolution: 30 arcsec (~1 km), 2.5 arcmin (~5 km)
Data layers: B01-19
attribution: Vanderwal, Jeremy. (2012). All future climate layers for Australia - 5km resolution. James Cook University.
